Sat Apr 25 03:25:41 UTC 2026 - Jonatas Gonçalves <jonatas.sgoncalves@gmail.com>

- Update to commit 5a49c3e4d717ffab1aabbf96e3c14dce3111d6d5:
  * Remove dependency on hcitool (deprecated in BlueZ 5).
  * Fix compatibility with Python 3.13 by replacing SafeConfigParser
